      <title>苹果报废汽车项目意味着人工智能和耳机赌注更加紧迫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/apple-cancels-its-electric-car-in-favor-of-ai-vision-pro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司放弃自动驾驶汽车计划，就等于放弃了数十亿美元的潜在收入，也放弃了销售一位高管所说的“终极移动设备”的梦想。希望是其他大赌注——包括生成式人工智能和混合现实耳机——可以弥补差额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/apple-cancels-its-electric-car-in-favor-of-ai-vision-pro</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国重新启动对应用材料公司中国业务的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-renews-inquiry-into-applied-materials-chinese-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府机构已发出新一轮要求，要求提供有关应用材料公司向中国客户发货的信息，在华盛顿试图切断向其地缘政治竞争对手销售先进芯片制造设备之际，这个敏感话题再次被提起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/us-renews-inquiry-into-applied-materials-chinese-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:08:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本田将在北美和日本销售插电式氢动力汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/honda-to-sell-plug-in-hydrogen-vehicle-in-north-america-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司将推出一款可充电的氢燃料电池汽车，成为第一家将该技术推向市场的日本汽车制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/honda-to-sell-plug-in-hydrogen-vehicle-in-north-america-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>百度需要抓住人工智能优势消除30%的跌幅：科技观察</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/baidu-needs-to-seize-ai-advantage-to-erase-30-drop-tech-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国互联网行业增长放缓，百度公司面临着一项关键考验，该公司需要证明自己能否利用其在人工智能领域的先发优势来重振其暴跌的股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/baidu-needs-to-seize-ai-advantage-to-erase-30-drop-tech-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果会见美国司法部反垄断主管，为避免预期的诉讼做最后的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/apple-met-with-justice-department-in-final-bid-to-avoid-antitrust-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司代表上周与司法部会面，试图说服该机构不要对该公司提起反垄断诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-27/apple-met-with-justice-department-in-final-bid-to-avoid-antitrust-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 23:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
